    "description": "<p>Mission</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Mission of the Home is to provide loving, Christian nurture for needy and disadvantaged children of all races and religions, so as to prepare them to be happy and responsible members of the family and community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vision</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To be a premier Children&rsquo;s Home and Centre where every child is nurtured to his/her full potential, ingrained with good Christian character to be happy and responsible members of their respective families and the community at large.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Goals</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. &nbsp;To develop the Spiritual, Educational, Social, Physical and</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Emotional well-being of the children.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. &nbsp;To provide an Inclusive Home environment to enhance the</p>\r\n\r\n<p>integration of children with special needs and mainstream children.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. &nbsp;To assist parents in problem-solving and coping with their</p>\r\n\r\n<p>difficulties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. &nbsp;To strengthen Family relationships and enhance the Quality of</p>\r\n\r\n<p>family life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
